 &#8216;@monteiro Vs @austinkleon FIGHT . https://t.co/47NoJQqxtC *(22:35:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Facebook Status Updates* Haha, @emzlinnett just Referred to Game of Thrones as &#8220;that Castle Thing with the midget&#8221;!Genius *(10:36:00)** Anyone Know Somewhere in Bristol I Could Buy Hide glue?The Bass Needs a Little Clamps N Glue Treatment Again *(10:44:00)** https://t.co/LFo1QhE0iV *(16:15:00)** *(22:07:00)** &#8216;@monteiro Vs @austinkleon FIGHT https://t.co/47NoJQqxtC *(22:35:00)** PSA: Been Running El Capitan since Last Week, no Issues with *anything*.Safari Keyboard Shortcuts Changed Though. Annoying. *(22:56:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Fitbit Statistics* Daily Activity Summary - *Total steps:* 19226, *Floors climbed:* , *Calories burned:* 3325, *Elevation gained:* Meters, *Traveled:* 15.38 Kilometers, *Sedentary minutes:* 693, *Lightly Active minutes:* 168, *Fairly Active minutes:* 52, *Very Active minutes:* 114 *(23:59:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Instapaper Article Saves* <a href=\"http://ift.tt/1GgEcmI\">5 Music Production Truisms that Are Actually nonsense</a> - Ask a Music Production or Theory Question on Any Internet Forum and you&#8217;ll Almost Certainly Receive an Authoritative-sounding Answer within Seconds from someone… *(22:54:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### New Twitter Followers* *Name:* <a href=\"http://twitter.com/FunnyAwkwardd\">Funny Awkward Moment</a>, *About:* Funny Awkward Moment Jokes, *Location:* *(23:53:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Tweets* Haha, @emzlinnett just Referred to Game of Thrones as &#8220;that Castle Thing with the midget&#8221;!Genius *(10:36:00)** Anyone Know Somewhere in Bristol I Could Buy Hide glue?The Bass Needs a Little Clamps N Glue Treatment Again *(10:44:00)** RT @thhamilton: The Daily Mail Last Year versus the Daily Mail This Year. http://t.co/4eCKfAVq8G *(11:27:00)** https://t.co/LFo1QhE0iV *(16:15:00)** &#8216;@monteiro Vs @austinkleon FIGHT https://t.co/47NoJQqxtC *(22:35:00)** RT @GYJARMY: TEASER ALERT!#littlewitchhttp://t.co/ieLos0icpb *(22:38:00)** RT @monteiro: ARE YOU KIDDING ME?!? THESE DIDN&#8217;T EXIST YET?!? MUST HAVE! https://t.co/ELdx6DHdIx *(22:50:00)** RT @Aly_Dodge: *** NEWS FLASH ***Mr Kipling Tells You to Steal cake… https://t.co/T8gVPmBunU *(22:52:00)** PSA: Been Running El Capitan since Last Week, no Issues with *anything*.Safari Keyboard Shortcuts Changed Though. Annoying. *(22:56:00)** @jonathanberger Cheers for that Dude! Appreciated. I Rely on Them for Firing Things into @omnifocus and @instapaper Pretty Regularly. *(23:30:00)** @danbenjamin I Whitelisted the Sites I like.Skip Podcasts Ads a Lot. I Have a Squarespace Site, Text Expander Etc, can&#8217;t Get harry&#8217;s in UK *(23:44:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Twitter Mentions* @doghousemike Does This Help? I Had the Same Issue. https://t.co/sirMDKM96J. *(Mentioned by jonathanberger)* *(23:01:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>","lines":[13,14],"size":3082,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
